thread.title_full: Car Mats UK reviewed by Victoria Murphy

author: Victoria Murphy
title: Victoria Murphy
text: We bought a new Kia Sportage which came with no car mats. Searched on Google for supplier and Car Mats UK was the first site to come up. The site is easy to use and I was surprised how reasonably priced the mats were. After reading the excellent reviews, I ordered the full set of mats for Â£29.99. The mats came within 3 days and we were very pleased with the quality and secure fit of the mats in the car. I am going to order a rubber boot mat this week so that my son's muddy football boots don't ruin the carpet. Thank you Car Mats UK - I will recommend you.
